item.spellbladenext.offering: 向六角刃法师提供服务
spell.spellbladenext.righteousfervor.des: 将火焰魔法中那毁灭性的一面展现出来！在效果持续时间内，你所释放的火焰法术将不再会被抗火效果影响！
spell.spellbladenext.risingflames.name: 新星之火
spell.spellbladenext.risingflames.descri: 对单个目标造成快速且逐渐增加的火焰伤害，每次伤害会为施法者叠加%5的施法速度和火焰法术威力。
spell.spellbladenext.ashes.name: 群星之遗
spell.spellbladenext.ashes.description: 被动：你的法术将会造成额外100%的寒冰法术伤害，拥有此效果时，每拥有两个寒冰或火焰法术将会使你获得一层奥秘注魔。主动：发动回旋击，造成{damage} 点寒冰伤害，按住shift以停止。
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyreflect.name: 撕裂飓风
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyreflect.descr: 掀起一阵飓风，每秒对单个目标造成{damage} 点物理伤害并击退目标。同时反弹来袭的弹射物。
spell.spellbladenext.frostborn.name: 永冻之地
spell.spellbladenext.frostborn.descripti: 以自己为中心，创造一片永冻之地。冻结其中生物两秒，或直至它们挣脱冻结（按shift挣脱）。
spell.spellbladenext.frostslam.name: 冰川重锤
spell.spellbladenext.frostslam.descripti: 使用寒冰属性武器进行重击，造成两倍近战伤害并提升惯性，伤害和施法速度。在获得惯性buff时，每一级buff会额外造成一点物理伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyspin.name: 美猴王之棍法
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyspin.descript: 发动回旋击，对范围内目标造成1.5倍的近战伤害。击中多个敌人会收到近战伤害惩罚。按住shift停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyslam.name: 美猴王之戏法
spell.spellbladenext.monkeyslam.descript: 遁入云层，在法术持续时间内无敌。
spell.spellbladenext.splitleft.name: 美猴王之分身
spell.spellbladenext.splitleft.descripti: 创造一个分身，并获得八秒隐身buff。分身会持续16秒，获得你攻击伤害的一半，攻击你最后八秒内攻击的敌人。在空闲时会跟着你。
spell.spellbladenext.backstab.name: 刺客
spell.spellbladenext.backstab.descriptio: 被动：背后的攻击是潜行攻击，一定触发法术暴击伤害。主动：对敌人释放，传送到他们身后并发动突袭。
spell.spellbladenext.steelblade.name: 纯化钢锭
spell.spellbladenext.steelblade.descript: 被动：命中时造成 {damage} 点的额外物理伤害。在暴击时，表现为法术而非普通攻击。
spell.spellbladenext.searingblade.name: 炽烈钢锭
spell.spellbladenext.searingblade.descri: 被动：击中时造成 {damage} 点的额外火焰伤害。在暴击时，表现为法术而非普通攻击。
spell.spellbladenext.gleamingblade.name: 辉耀钢锭
spell.spellbladenext.gleamingblade.descr: 被动：命中时造成 {damage} 点的额外奥秘伤害。在暴击时，表现为法术而非普通攻击。
spell.spellbladenext.frozenblade.name: 冷钢
spell.spellbladenext.frozenblade.descrip: 被动：命中时造成 {damage} 点的额外寒冰伤害。在暴击时，表现为法术而非普通攻击。
spell.spellbladenext.inferno.name: 地狱
spell.spellbladenext.inferno.description: 被动：击中时造成100%的火焰伤害，可暴击。主动：向一个方向旋转，每秒对附近的敌人造成 {damage} 点的火焰伤害。击中敌人，给予你附体效果，最高5级。Shift键停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.2hslam.name: 碎骨
spell.spellbladenext.2hslam.description: 使用武器进行重击，造成两倍近战伤害并提升惯性，伤害和施法速度。在获得惯性buff时，每一级buff会额外造成一点物理伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.1hslam.name: 碎骨
spell.spellbladenext.1hslam.description: 使用武器进行重击，造成两倍近战伤害并提升惯性，伤害和施法速度。在获得惯性buff时，每一级buff会额外造成一点物理伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.riposte.name: 花刀
spell.spellbladenext.riposte.description: 在你周围一圈造成1.5倍近战伤害。伤害将乘以你附体层数的20倍，并消耗附体层数。
spell.spellbladenext.roll.name: 战术突进
spell.spellbladenext.roll.description: 向前向前突进，格挡受到的攻击。突进结束后对目标进行反击，造成1.5倍的伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.whirlwind.name: 利刃回旋
spell.spellbladenext.whirlwind.descripti: 发动回旋击，对附近敌人造成三倍近战伤害。击中多个目标会受到伤害惩罚。法术强化的20%将倍强化到攻击上。按住shift以停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.dualwield_whirlwind: 发动回旋击，对附近敌人造成(1.5倍)或双持(可变)的近战伤害。击中多个目标会受到伤害惩罚。法术强化的20%将倍强化到攻击上。按住shift以停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.whirlwind_polearm.d: Spin, dealing 3x melee dps to nearby enemies. Penalty for hitting multiple enemies. 0.2x modifier for spell on hit effects. Shift to stop moving.
spell.spellbladenext.cyclone.name: 飓风
spell.spellbladenext.cyclone.description: 被动：击中时造成100%的寒冰伤害，可暴击。主动：向一个方向旋转，每秒对附近的敌人造成 {damage} 点的寒冰伤害。击中敌人，给予你灌注效果，最高5级。Shift键停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.maelstrom.name: Maelstrom
spell.spellbladenext.maelstrom.descripti: 被动：击中时造成100%的奥秘伤害，可暴击。主动：向一个方向旋转，每秒对附近的敌人造成 {damage} 点的奥秘伤害。击中敌人，给予你注魔效果，最高5级。Shift键停止移动。
spell.spellbladenext.coldfury.name: Frost Flurry
spell.spellbladenext.coldfury.descriptio: Project a frozen statue in the direction you are facing, which stops after a certain distance or when it collides with something, dealing {damage} frost damage repeatedly.
spell.spellbladenext.multicoldfury.name: 寒冰军团
spell.spellbladenext.multicoldfury.descr: Project four frozen statue in four different directions, each one stops after a certain distance or when it collides with something, dealing {damage} frost damage repeatedly.
spell.spellbladenext.fireoverdrive.name: 烈焰过载
spell.spellbladenext.fireoverdrive.descr: Perform a nova, dealing {damage} fire damage to enemies around you, and giving yourself a stacking attack speed buff. Can be triggered on hit.
spell.spellbladenext.frostoverdrive.name: 冰霜过载
spell.spellbladenext.frostoverdrive.desc: Perform a nova, dealing {damage} frost damage to enemies around you, and giving yourself a stacking attack speed buff. Can be triggered on hit.
spell.spellbladenext.arcaneoverdrive.des: Perform a nova, dealing {damage} arcane damage to enemies around you, and giving yourself a stacking attack speed buff. Can be triggered on hit.
spell.spellbladenext.fireinfusion.name: 火焰灌注
spell.spellbladenext.fireinfusion.descri: Passive: You deal 2/3 of your fire attribute on hit. Can crit. Active: Infuse your sword, gaining a stacking +2 fire attribute buff. This buff stacks and refreshes on hit up to 3 times.
spell.spellbladenext.frostinfusion.name: 寒冰灌注
spell.spellbladenext.frostinfusion.descr: Passive: You deal 2/3 of your frost attribute on hit. Can crit. Active: Infuse your sword, gaining a stacking +2 frost attribute buff. This buff stacks and refreshes on hit, up to 3 times.
spell.spellbladenext.arcaneinfusion.name: 奥秘灌注
spell.spellbladenext.arcaneinfusion.desc: Passive: You deal 2/3 of your arcane attribute on hit. Can crit. Active: Infuse your sword, gaining a stacking +2 arcane attribute buff. This buff stacks and refreshes on hit up to 3 times.
spell.spellbladenext.magic_missile.name: 魔法导弹
spell.spellbladenext.magic_missile.descr: Shoot a projectile that shortly splits into three homing projectile. These projectiles target the three closest enemies if no target is chosen. Each projectile deals {damage} damage.
spell.spellbladenext.shadeslash.name: Arcane Twinslash
spell.spellbladenext.shadeslash.descript: Slash around you at your location as well as at the targeted location, dealing {damage} arcane damage per slash.
spell.spellbladenext.multislash.name: 多段打击
spell.spellbladenext.multislash.descript: Slash around you at your location as well as at two locations 2 blocks forward and to each side, dealing {damage} arcane damage per slash.
spell.spellbladenext.opportunity.name: Opportunity Attack
spell.spellbladenext.opportunity.descrip: Raise your shield and weapon in a defensive stance, blocking front attacks. If an enemy moves in front of you, it and nearby enemies are dealth 2x melee damage.
spell.spellbladenext.transmute_fire.name: Transmute Copper
spell.spellbladenext.transmute_fire.desc: 将一个铜块转化为四个火焰符文锭
spell.spellbladenext.transmute_frost.des: 将一个铁块转化为四个寒冰符文锭
spell.spellbladenext.transmute_arcane.de: 将一个金块转化为四个闪耀符文锭
spell.spellbladenext.soulfire.name: 灵魂燃烧
spell.spellbladenext.soulfire.descriptio: 刷新并获得一层灵魂燃烧，持续 10 秒。每叠加一次灵魂燃烧，就能获得 1 点额外火焰法术威力。当你的灵魂燃烧层数超过 5 层时，你就会受到燃烧伤害，并且每秒每层受到的燃烧伤害都会增加。
spell.spellbladenext.mulberry.name: 桑葚是一种树，它会……
spell.spellbladenext.mulberry.descriptio: Conjure your Spirit Sword. Gain a stack of Burning Spirit for 10 seconds.
spell.spellbladenext.magma_orb.name: 岩浆球
spell.spellbladenext.magma_orb.descripti: Launch a Magma Orb that deals {damage} fire damage in an area when it bounces.
spell.spellbladenext.sonic_boom.name: 音爆
spell.spellbladenext.sonic_boom.descript: Unleash a Sonic Boom in the targeted direction, dealing {damage} arcane damage to enemies in a straight line.
spell.spellbladenext.glacial_barrage.des: Launch a barrage of Icicles as you channel, dealing {damage} frost damage per second.
spell.spellbladenext.horizontal_eruption: Unleash a devastating wave of embers. Each flame deals {damage} fire damage.
spell.spellbladenext.vertical_eruption.d: Unleash a devastating column of embers. Each flame deals {damage} fire damage
spell.spellbladenext.icicle_barrier.name: 冰暴
spell.spellbladenext.icicle_barrier.desc: Create Icicles that orbit you in a spiral, dealing {damage} frost damage every 0.5 seconds and disappearing after 2 seconds.
spell.spellbladenext.arctic_winds.name: 北极风雪
spell.spellbladenext.arctic_winds.descri: Enter a stance that releases glacial winds expanding outwards from your location, dealing {damage} frost damage every second.
spell.spellbladenext.amethyst_rain.name: 紫水晶暴雨
spell.spellbladenext.amethyst_rain.descr: Launch four Amethysts into the air that slow down to a halt, and then home into the nearest enemy, each dealing {damage} arcane damage.
spell.spellbladenext.flicker_strike.name: Flickering Flame
spell.spellbladenext.flicker_strike.desc: Teleport to the nearest enemy, striking them repeatedly for 1x melee DPS if they are the only enemy nearby. If there are more enemies nearby, you teleport to all of them equally. 0.2x modifier for spell on hit effects.
spell.spellbladenext.flame_winds.name: 「烈日狂风」
spell.spellbladenext.flame_winds.descrip: Launch a sphere of scorching air in a direction, dealing {damage} fire damage per second to enemies caught in it and carrying them in the direction of the wind.
spell.spellbladenext.endersgaze.name: 末影凝视
spell.spellbladenext.endersgaze.descript: 发射一颗缓慢移动的末影珍珠。被击中的第一个敌人会被5个旋转的末影之眼环绕4秒，每个末影之眼每五分之二秒会造成 {damage} 点奥术伤害。末影之眼在敌人死亡就会脱离，如果寻找到新的宿主则会刷新其持续时间。
spell.spellbladenext.visionofender.name: 末影视线
spell.spellbladenext.visionofender.descr: 附近的敌人会被5个旋转的末影之眼环绕2秒，每个末影之眼每五分之二秒会造成 {damage} 点奥术伤害。末影之眼在敌人死亡就会脱离，如果寻找到新的宿主则会刷新其持续时间。
spell.spellbladenext.supernova.name: 超新星
spell.spellbladenext.supernova.descripti: 在你的位置充能并释放一颗破坏力巨大的超新星，对这片区域的敌人造成 {damage} 点火焰伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.snowball_bombardmen: Channel to summon three snowballs that rotate around you every 1/4 second. These snowballs orbit once and then launch themsenves into the sky towards a random enemy in the direction you are looking, dealing {damage} frost damage.
spell.spellbladenext.chain.name: 连锁
spell.spellbladenext.chain.description: Your arrows chain to nearby enemies twice, possibly hitting the first enemy twice.
spell.spellbladenext.multishot.name: 分裂箭
spell.spellbladenext.multishot.descripti: 当你射出一支箭时，最多会向附近的敌人多射两支箭。
spell.spellbladenext.primordialburst.des: 33% chance on arrow hit to trigger an elemental nova. Each element has a separate 2 second cooldown.
spell.spellbladenext.barrage.name: 雹暴
spell.spellbladenext.barrage.description: Channel to continuously shoot arrows. These arrows deal base physical projectile damage equal to your Frost power. This bow can contain up to two additional effects via the Spell Binding Table.
spell.spellbladenext.explosion.name: 燃尽
spell.spellbladenext.explosion.descripti: 在目标地点或目标敌人处召唤一次延时的爆炸，向爆炸中心周围除你以外所有的敌人造成最多 {damage} 点伤害。
spell.spellbladenext.defiance.name: 顽强不屈
spell.spellbladenext.defiance.descriptio: 被击中时，你将获得一级生命恢复效果，最高Ⅳ级，持续2秒。使用以立即获得持续2秒的生命恢复Ⅳ。在冷却时不会被动生效。
spell.spellbladenext.courage.name: 勇气
spell.spellbladenext.courage.description: 你会被动获得最高Ⅲ级的抗性提升，每4秒一级。被击中会使你失去一级抗性提升的效果。使用以立即获得抗性提升Ⅲ。在冷却时不会被动生效。
spell.spellbladenext.determination.name: 决心
spell.spellbladenext.determination.descr: 给你一大堆战斗buff。如果你死亡时不在冷却期间，会造成更长的冷却时间来避免你死亡，同时给你增加8秒的buff。8秒后你将受到严重伤害。
enchantment.spellbladenext.spellshield.d: 释放你的主手法术来阻挡从正面攻击的人。
